Summary
----------------------------------------------------------------
The greeter project has no external NuGet packages, so dotnet
restore completed almost instantly (63 ms). However, the NuGet
proxy was still contacted — ngrok logs showed SDK workload check
requests hitting the Nexus nuget-proxy endpoint. This confirms
the proxy plumbing is active even when the project itself has
no third-party dependencies.

The exporter step succeeded, confirming the mount-path fix
(secret mounted at /home/cnb/.nuget/NuGet/NuGet.Config) is
working correctly.

